text: Sanaa Koubaa (born 6 January 1985 in Langenfeld) is a German athlete competing in the 3000 metres steeplechase. She represented her country at the 2016 Summer Olympics without qualifying for the final. ==International competitions== {| |- !colspan="6"|Representing |- |2012 |European Championships |Helsinki, Finland |13th |3000 m s'chase |10:02.33 |- |2016 |Olympic Games |Rio de Janeiro, Brazil |27th (h) |3000 m s'chase |9:35.15 |} ==Personal bests== Outdoor *1500 metres – 4:13.48 (Leuven 2016) *3000 metres – 9:20.65 (Bergisch Gladbach 2015) *5000 metres – 16:40.42 (Koblenz 2011) *3000 metres steeplechase – 9:35.15 (Rio de Janeiro 2016) Indoor *1500 metres – 4:27.00 (Leverkusen 2012) *3000 metres – 9:30.87 (Leverkusen 2012) ==References== Category:Living people Category:1985 births Category:German people of Moroccan descent Category:German female steeplechase runners Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Germany Category:People from Mettmann (district)
